|                                                                         |
| 1) Create 2 payment buttons: a payment button from PayPal, or any       |
| payment system that uses PayPal such as JVZoo, Warrior+, DigiResults    |
| or Zaxxa, and then anoher payment button for Clickbank.                 |
|                                                                         |
| 2) Add a WP-VATSLAP shortcode to any WordPress post/page...and that's   |
| it! Then if a visitor arrives to your page from a country where a       |
| sale would normally involve charging VAT on a purchase WP-VATSLAP       |
| will show them the Clickbank payment button...otherwise WP-VATSLAP      |
| will show your regular JVZoo, Warrior+ (or whatever payment procesor    |
